metadata.name: 1. Amazonius Prime
metadata.description:
Amazonius Prime

The samurai like warrior scours the commercial landscape for unsuspecting businesses to gut. Thick cardboard armour shields it from tax laws and covers up some questionable labour practices and its Prime Package Cannon yeets packages of consumer goods at an inhuman rate. Alexa, it’s ‘friendly’ servant, keeps an all hearing ear in the homes of its usres whilst it tramples high streets propelled by the phalic, blue rocket ships of its founder, lord Bezos.

Attributes:

- Retail slaying sword
- Thick cardboard armour
- Drone delivery service
- Amazonius web services power source
- Kindle chest plate armor
- Prime package cannon
- Algorythmically run slave warehouses
- Blue rocket propulsion

The Tech Giants is an ongoing series of artworks depicting the big tech companies as giant robots.
